<br>
I don't know if the items are droppable because I haven't looted them personally and never asked, but since they all require multiple items, even if they were no drop they could be MQed.  My suspicion is that at least one of the quest items is droppable, but someone please correct me if I'm wrong (I just think it would be stupid to make them all no-drop on quests like these, just like it would have been stupid to make all the Velious armor quest gems no-drop).<br>
<br>
