verfish</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Knight Of the Realm</span><br>  Posts: 806<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(3/28/02 7:47:42 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathholyswordsandquests.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3421.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: ToV quests</span><hr size=1> by chance how do you guys decide who gets what?<br>
